Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.56,0:01:39.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm back, Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.39,0:01:41.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is the bath water hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:44.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have to hurry or I'll be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:46.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it so serious that she\ncan't have visitors?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:47.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:51.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes... Kagome is laid\nup in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:52.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.04,0:01:55.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... This is a hot compress\nfor Kagome...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.91,0:01:58.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, you're so thoughtful!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:03.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My... I mean, her neuralgia\nwill get much better with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:05.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll be going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:08.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay, take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.22,0:02:12.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who has neuralgia?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:14.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, Kagome!\NBe happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:18.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're supposed to be disposed today,\nso you can miss school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.93,0:02:23.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!\NI WANT to go to school desperately!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.67,0:02:25.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're a strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.64,0:02:30.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only my family knows of my\njaunts through the hidden well...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:32.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}into the Feudal States Era.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:37.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Besides, I doubt that anyone else\nwould believe me if I told them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.27,0:02:59.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? You're going to take the\nmath supplement course, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:01.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Teacher told me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:06.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're used to it, but it's a shock\nto hear that you need it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:09.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The high school Hojo is applying to\nis very difficult to get into.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:13.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? Don't tell me you're\nseeing Hojo, Kagome?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:18.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop it! Who has time to\ngo out with boys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:21.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's not something\nyou want to brag about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:21.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:26.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gee, I don't even know if\NI'll be able to get into high school!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:27.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not with a life like this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:30.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, look!\NFireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:31.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:33.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It looks like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:37.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:56.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ha-ha-ha! Serves them right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:03:58.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.73,0:04:02.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:08.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What did you do that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:11.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You... You can see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:14.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who is this girl?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:16.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where're her shoes?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:21.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And a down jacket...\nwhen it's almost summer?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:25.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go apologize.\NI'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:27.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,None of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.71,0:04:45.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:46.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who were you talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:47.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.98,0:04:53.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gone... Who was she?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:03.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Myoga, isn't it finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.56,0:05:05.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:09.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Inuyasha, if you go out now,\nyou'll be stung to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:15.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That sheathe was cracked\nbattling the Thunder Brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:18.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let the steel wasps repair it\nwith their special wax.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.68,0:05:21.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dang it... It's boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:24.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:29.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I came along because I thought\NKagome would be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:33.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why must I be stuck\nalone with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:34.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:38.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Arghh... Why am I alone\nwith you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:39.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:42.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't I count at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:43.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:47.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:48.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A goblin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:51.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo... So are you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.81,0:05:54.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's the Soul Piper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:57.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was born from the souls\nof departed children.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:01.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When a child dies, the Soul Piper\nplays with that child...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.52,0:06:03.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,until the soul is able to\nrest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:07.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As long as its eyes are closed,\nit's a peaceful demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:17.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! Not when I've come\nback to this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:22.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jeepers! Why do I have to\naccompany you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:24.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to visit YOUR friend\nin the hospital?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:27.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because the hospital's in\nthe next town...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:29.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and Mom's too busy to\ntake me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:33.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cripes! Everyone's interfering\nwith my studies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:35.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.36,0:06:37.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.36,0:06:39.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is there such a thing\nas an evil spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:41.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sota, thank you for coming\nso often.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:48.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aunty, how is Satoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.14,0:06:50.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Physically, he's healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:53.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But he's still unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:54.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:58.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for\nworrying about Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:00.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Burn scars?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:02.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh these...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:04.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I got them from the fire\nsix months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:06.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:07.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's how Satoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:22.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:25.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The girl at the park...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:28.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She disappeared!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:31.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Again... Why must this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.71,0:07:33.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who is she anyway?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:37.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't ignore this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:47.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Darn, foiled again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:53.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mentioned an evil spirit.\NWhat did you mean, Sota?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:57.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought maybe an evil spirit\nwas after Satoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.07,0:08:02.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Satoru has been in a coma\nsince the fire six months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:06.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At first, all my classmates went\nto visit him at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:07.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:09.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,weird things happened\non their way home...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:11.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,like falling down the stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:13.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,or barely missing getting hit\nby a car...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:19.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After these things kept happening,\nthe kids stayed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:22.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In that fire six months ago,\nshe died...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:24.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Satoru's older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.26,0:08:26.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Her name was Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.10,0:08:29.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Is that the place?\N- Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:32.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whenever they tried to\nclean up after the fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:34.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,an accident would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.14,0:08:36.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So it's been like that\nfor six months now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:39.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:45.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I knew it!\NThere is an evil spirit!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:47.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sota!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:51.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!\NWatch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:08:59.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid!\NI'm already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:02.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're Mayu, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:05.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do you do\nthese things?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:07.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aren't you Satoru's sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.07,0:09:10.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Satoru, hah! I'll kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:13.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mom hated me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:16.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why she abandoned me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:19.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She never wanted me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.82,0:09:25.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mayu... She seems so nice.\NDon't make her unhappy anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:26.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:30.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you keep interfering,\NI'll kill you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:31.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:49.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:56.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Until my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:00.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,are open?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:07.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"Until my eyes are open"?\NWhat does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:13.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So that demon is called\nthe Soul Piper?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.54,0:10:16.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh... So you have it\nin your world, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:19.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's supposed to console the\nsouls of dead children.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.31,0:10:25.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It plays its flute\nuntil the souls find peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:28.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And if the soul cannot\nfind peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:30.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If the soul has regrets\nor harbors a grudge...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:33.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then that spirit becomes\nan evil spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:34.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Evil spirit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:38.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When regrets turn to rage\nand hatred in a spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:39.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,it becomes evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:41.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Upon becoming an evil spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:44.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the Soul Piper hurls it\ninto the depths of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:49.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When the Soul Piper's eyes\nare fully open, it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:51.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't allow that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:53.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mayu must find peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:54.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forget it, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:58.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ghosts are different\nfrom demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:01.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can't just slay them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.85,0:11:03.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,One misstep and you'll regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:05.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I can't ignore it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:07.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I come from a shrine family!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:09.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There must be something\NI can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:14.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Well, count me out of this one!\NThere's nothing in it for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:18.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome is already gone.\NFool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:21.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't ignore her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:25.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That girl has so much\nsadness in her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:38.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mom, I want a cotton kimono\nwith goldfish on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.93,0:11:41.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When the summer comes,\NI'll go to the fairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.33,0:11:43.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and catch lots and lots\nof his goldfish friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:45.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want to wear my\ncotton kimono then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:48.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mayu, summer's a long\nways off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:50.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's okay.\NPromise?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.47,0:11:51.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:02.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When Mom leaves the\nhospital tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:04.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going to kill her\ndear, little Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:21.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're going home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:24.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll see you again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:25.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,0:12:27.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:30.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, you're Sota's sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:34.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Umm... About Satoru's\nlate sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:41.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for you!\NPlease go around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:48.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That day...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:52.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:54.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why didn't you come\nto the Open House?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:56.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It couldn't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:12:58.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Satoru's temperature\nshot up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:01.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All you care about\nis Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:02.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:04.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hate you and Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:06.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mayu, just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:07.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:13.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We always had arguments\nlike that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:18.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,On that day, when Mayu ran off...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:20.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought,\N"Oh, there she goes again."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:22.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:55.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I had known that\NMayu was inside the apartment...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:02.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A child!\NPoor thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:06.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I had known, I would\nhave gone back...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:08.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I had only known!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:13.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She wasn't aware that Mayu\nwas inside during the fire.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:16.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's Satoru's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:17.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:23.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mayu, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:30.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,M-Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:31.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:31.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:37.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mayu, think hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.80,0:14:40.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did your mother really\nabandon you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:46.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe she didn't know you were\ninside the apartment during that fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:51.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Brrr... It was cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:57.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sis... You're not supposed to\nhang things above the heater...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:14:58.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,when Mom is not at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:14:59.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.73,0:15:07.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you dare tell Mom that\NI'm hiding here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:09.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want to make her worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:14.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That muffler caught on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:15.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.11,0:15:17.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mom's not to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.71,0:15:18.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even Satoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:21.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.62,0:15:26.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I... I... I know that!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:32.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.46,0:15:36.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:38.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:41.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cripes! I can't stand\nto watch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.47,0:15:45.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:48.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You came!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:51.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you\nnot to get involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.15,0:15:55.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's too late for that\nlittle kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:16:01.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Making her realize the truth\ndoesn't mean she'll find peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:02.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It ain't that simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.93,0:16:07.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! The eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:13.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aghh! What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:15.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:24.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Remember this! I don't know\nanything about ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:26.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you work it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:31.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I must help Mayu find peace\nbefore she falls into hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:32.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is what Myoga said...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.29,0:16:36.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the Soul Piper takes the spirit\nto the spot where the death occurred...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:39.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,then drags it down into hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:47.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look over there!\NSeems pretty dangerous to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:53.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, let me off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:57.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool! Did you really think\nyou can manage alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:16:59.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No wonder they say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.65,0:17:02.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,there's nothing scarier\nthan an ignoramus!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:08.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh that's right... This is where\nhumans get sucked into hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:12.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Only humans like Kagome can\nproceed any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:15.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! This is one time\NI'm totally helpless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:20.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's pitch black.\NWhere am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:23.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A light?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.74,0:17:33.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!\NYou're conscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.91,0:17:36.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Umm... What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:38.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Never mind... Look at Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:39.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.15,0:17:41.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:45.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:51.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mom... Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:54.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sis is inside the closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:57.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please hurry and get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:06.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is how I died.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:12.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I couldn't be saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.58,0:18:13.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:15.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:17.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who is that?! Mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:18.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:19.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:22.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:25.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry! Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.13,0:18:30.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you crazy?!\NI'm already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.07,0:18:32.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't have a home anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:40.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:49.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:18:58.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're going home, Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:19:00.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're going home and\nmake peace with your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.14,0:19:12.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your mother loves you so\nvery much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:19.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it okay if you never\nsee her again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:26.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's not angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:31.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mom's not angry at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:39.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you worry.\NShe's your mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.98,0:19:47.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Try to remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.18,0:19:50.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,about your mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:19:59.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:03.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want to see you one more time,\nso I can say I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:08.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wanted to make up with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:35.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.17,0:20:44.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:46.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:49.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.48,0:20:52.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:55.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:00.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.63,0:21:10.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hope it worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.40,0:21:14.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cripes! You get into\nsuch scrapes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.30,0:21:17.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,One wrong move and you'd\nhave been dragged into hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,with that impish evil spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.04,0:21:22.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Evil spirit...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:28.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}One week later, Satoru was\nreleased from the hospital.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.42,0:21:31.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:36.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.72,0:21:38.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wanted to thank you\nbefore I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.29,0:21:42.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Such a pretty cotton kimono!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.16,0:21:44.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mom sewed it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.43,0:21:47.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything.\NBye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.84,0:21:57.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mayu, you weren't meant\nto be an evil spirit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:22:02.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You were just a little girl\nwho loved her mother very much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.15,0:23:49.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha... Half-demon and\nhalf-human.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.25,0:23:52.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha's goal is to gather\nthe fragments of the Sacred Jewel...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.59,0:23:54.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to become a full-fledged demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.46,0:23:56.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,During our search for the fragments...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.33,0:23:58.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,we come to the rescue of a\ngirl named Nazuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.60,0:24:01.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She takes us to spend the night\nat an old temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.13,0:24:04.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Spider Lord lurks in\nthe shadows... Is it a trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.54,0:24:07.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But on this moonless night,\na secret weakness is revealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.11,0:24:08.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.11,0:24:12.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"The Mystery of the New Moon and\nthe Black-haired Inuyasha!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.31,0:24:13.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
